<br>
• Israel evacuates all of its missions around the world.<br>
<br>
• The Centers for Disease Control and Prevention in Atlanta is evacuated. CDC prepares bioterrorism teams in case they become necessary.<br>
<br>
• Philadelphia landmarks are evacuated.<br>
<br>
• In Chicago, the Sears Tower is evacuated; United Nations in New York is evacuated. <br>
<br>
• Five battleships and two aircraft are deployed along the East Coast of the United States, and two aircraft carriers go to New York area, all from Norfolk, Virginia.<br>
<br>
